title: San Francisco/Fisherman's Wharf
name: USS Pampanito Submarine
directions: at Taylor St and the Embarcadero
hours: Opens at 9AM daily. Call for closing time
price: $10 adults, $6 seniors, $4 children/active military, free for children under 6. $20 for family of 2 adults and 4 children
content: This is a National Historic Landmark —  an authentic WWII submarine with many original artifacts on display. Up to 80 personnel ran this submarine and it could be at sea for up to several weeks at a time.
